<br>
This is what I will go for:<br>
<br>
First Aid II -&gt; 9 rp<br>
Ignore Pain -&gt; 8 rp<br>
Purge -&gt; 4 rp<br>
Aug Dex II -&gt; 4 rp<br>
Master of Pain II -&gt; 4 rp<br>
<br>
Then I will be RR3L9... and have no clue what to do then...<br>
<br>
Determination?<br>
Mastery of Parry?<br>
Dodger? (I really hate to spend 4 points for aug qui II)<br>
More MoPain?<br>
Avoidance of Magic?<br>
Long Wind?<br>
<br>
Any input welcome...<br>
<br>
Thanks in advance <p>Halbarad GimpMaster, Bladesong, RR2L4, Excalibur</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=halbaradaglardin>Halbarad Aglardin</A> at: 12/6/02 9:45:10 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tklausing>tklausing</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Professional Board Spammer</span><br>  Posts: 29<br> <font color=#000000>(12/6/02 11:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=60.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://tklausing.home.attbi.com/image/disco.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Realm Abilities</span><hr size=1> That is a good beginning route. After you have all the ones listed to get you to 3L9, you probably want to get Determination 2 or 3 asap.<br>
<br>
From there, look at these RA's (in this order):<br>
<br>
Aug Con 2<br>
Toughness 2<br>
Aug Qui 2<br>
Dodger 2<br>
Avoidance of Magic 1 or 2<br>
Mastery of Parrying 2<br>
<br>
Other cheap RA's to consider, depending on your playstyle:<br>
<br>
Longwind 1 (if you sprint a lot)<br>
Tireless 1 (to regen endurance while moving/attacking)<br>
Lifter 1 (if you want to carry a full ram)<br>
<br>
Note: I didn't list Dualist's reflexes because I am still for the most part iffy on that skill, not sure how useful it is.<br>
<br>
Here is how I am doing my RA spec:<br>
<br>
FA2/IP<br>
Purge<br>
Aug Con 2<br>
Toughness 2<br>
Aug Dex 2<br>
Mastery of Pain 2<br>
Determination 2<br>
Aug Qui 2<br>
Dodger 2<br>
Long Wind 1<br>
AoM 2<br>
Master of Parrying 2<br>
Duelist's Reflexes 2 <p>========== <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Dark Age of Camelot</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> ==========<br>
